00:12:44.928 --> 00:12:46.649
Judaism and the Torah.
 

00:12:46.649 --> 00:12:50.909
What does the Torah,
the Law, mean in Matthew?

00:12:50.909 --> 00:12:54.615
Look at 5:17;
