00:17:44.799 --> 00:17:49.277
Look at 5:38:
"You have heard that it

00:17:49.277 --> 00:17:51.750
was said an eye for an eye,
and a tooth for a tooth,

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:53.690
but I say do not resist an evil
doer.

00:17:53.690 --> 00:17:56.085
If anyone strikes you on the
