Jesus is doing away with this

00:18:12.796 --> 00:18:15.032
bad,
strict, legalism of the Jewish

00:18:15.032 --> 00:18:17.980
law,
and he's teaching you a law of

00:18:17.980 --> 00:18:20.078
grace,
instead, and forgiveness.

00:18:20.078 --> 00:18:21.960
That's not what's going on
