00:23:12.380 --> 00:23:16.251
Verse 13, "When Jesus came
from the district of Caesarea of

00:23:16.251 --> 00:23:17.769
Philippi,
he asked his disciples,

00:23:17.769 --> 00:23:19.059
"Who do you say that I
